WEBVTT

00:00:00.713 --> 00:00:03.422
Ovako smo putovali 1900. godine.

00:00:03.422 --> 00:00:05.791
To je otvoreni jednopreg. Nema grijanje.

00:00:05.791 --> 00:00:07.420
Nema klima uređaj.

00:00:07.420 --> 00:00:09.477
Vuče ga konj

00:00:09.477 --> 00:00:11.775
brzinom koja iznosi jedan posto brzine zvuka,

00:00:11.775 --> 00:00:13.527
i izborana zemljana cesta

00:00:13.527 --> 00:00:17.909
pretvara se u blatnu močvaru svaki put kad kiši.

00:00:17.909 --> 00:00:20.654
Ovo je Boeing 707.

00:00:20.654 --> 00:00:22.955
Samo 60 godina kasnije, on putuje

00:00:22.955 --> 00:00:25.172
na 80 posto brzine zvuka

00:00:25.172 --> 00:00:27.805
i danas ne putujemo ništa brže

00:00:27.805 --> 00:00:30.944
jer se komercijalno supersončino putovanje zrakom